# Adder

## Overview
Implements addition between two input operands.

## Board
Arty A7 (Artix-7)

## Tools
- Verilog
- Xilinx Vivado

## Description
This design performs binary addition of two inputs and produces the result as output.

## Inputs
- Operand A
- Operand B

## Outputs
- Sum

## Notes
Demonstrates basic combinational logic and arithmetic design using Verilog.
